OL,3,CFamily of woman killed in crash
OL,4,Cdescribe 'immeasurable void' left in
OL,5,Ctheir lives
OL,7,FThe family of a woman who died in a
OL,8,Fcrash on the A338 in Wiltshire says
OL,9,Fshe was a "fun, warm person who
OL,10,Fbrought laughter to those around her."
OL,12,FSara-Louise Brown, 43, died when the
OL,13,FMini Cooper she was driving left the
OL,14,Fcarriageway and rolled onto its roof
OL,15,Fat Collingbourne Ducis on Salisbury
OL,16,Fplain.
OL,18,FNo other vehicle was involved in the
OL,19,Fcrash.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
