OL,3,CFamily of woman killed in crash
OL,4,Cdescribe 'immeasurable void' left in
OL,5,Ctheir lives
OL,7,FIn a statement, her family said: "The
OL,8,Ffamily of Sara-Louise Brown/Burton/
OL,9,FMcpherson are devastated to announce
OL,10,Fshe sadly passed in a road traffic
OL,11,Faccident on Wednesday 15th April.
OL,13,F"Sara was a much-loved mother,
OL,14,Fgrandmother, daughter, sister and
OL,15,Ffriend.
OL,17,F"She was a fun, warm person who
OL,18,Fbrought laughter to those around her,
OL,19,Fand her loss has left an immeasurable
OL,20,Fvoid in all of our lives.
