OL,3,CFamily of woman killed in crash
OL,4,Cdescribe 'immeasurable void' left in
OL,5,Ctheir lives
OL,7,F"The family would like to thank the
OL,8,Femergency services and all those who
OL,9,Fhave offered support in this difficult
OL,10,Ftime."
